{"tid":1550802,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"絲打跳閘攻略","createTime":"2019-09-07T17:45:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T04:41:39.000Z","uid":261198,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"025a720a80f43746a2b05644cf965de5e78273d4","tid":1550802,"uid":261198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:45:50.000Z","msg":"俾想跳又唔夠膽跳嘅絲睇<br />\n帶定絲巾圍巾包上身<br />\n可以扎埋頭髮戴口罩<br />\n條絲巾有幾突出得咁突出<br />\n為嘅就係要去跳嘅一刻令佢留下深刻印象<br />\n然後就一路跑一路除身上嘅裝<br />\n放頭髮收埋絲巾除口罩<br />\n之後啲小粉紅就會掛住搵頭先見到嘅顏色而漠視左你㗎啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"292d4a31418b3e85019f67ebfcbd9a81e51f524e","tid":1550802,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:46:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9e9df50e2739aaf3495b69761eebd0a4799a5f73","tid":1550802,"uid":69294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:49:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"837f7c0d3c7dd6c8e503d037de8d28eb26f8fbf4","tid":1550802,"uid":261198,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9e9df50e2739aaf3495b6